data.description: No HOA restrictions ** Motivated Sellers - Will entertain all reasonable offers ** This spacious single-family residence features 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a fantastic location close to all of Sarasota's amenities, including the renowned Siesta Key Beach. This home has ample space for your family and the ability to personalize and make it your own. Enjoy the convenience of a newer kitchen, complete with modern appliances and stylish cabinetry. Step outside to your private backyard. Whether you're dreaming of a lush garden, a relaxing patio, or a play area, this outdoor space provides a canvas for your imagination. You're just a short drive away from shopping centers, restaurants, parks, and cultural attractions. Sarasota offers a vibrant arts scene, championship golf courses, and countless recreational activities for all ages. Transform this gem into your dream home or an investment opportunity. Schedule your showing today and start turning your Sarasota dreams into reality!
